 * lanes.lane_1_desc => 路线1描述:textarea:Visible stakes, clear chip prompts, and the fastest route into regular blackjack tables.
 * lanes.lane_2_label => 路线2标签:text:Live Route
 * lanes.lane_2_title => 路线2标题:text:Dealer-Led Tables
 * lanes.lane_2_desc => 路线2描述:textarea:A cleaner path to live sessions with seat cues and pace notes surfaced earlier.
